OL,3,CAncient ritual of blowing into shell
OL,4,C'could help with common sleep disorder'
OL,6,FThe small trial, led by researchers in
OL,7,FIndia, involved 30 people aged with 19
OL,8,Fand 65 with OSA.
OL,10,FOSA happens with the walls of the
OL,11,Fthroat relax and narrow or close, with
OL,12,Fsymptoms including choking noises,
OL,13,Floud snoring and waking up a lot.
OL,15,FThe condition is thought to impact
OL,16,Fabout eight million people in the UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
