OL,3,CAncient ritual of blowing into shell
OL,4,C'could help with common sleep disorder'
OL,6,FFor the trial, 16 people were provided
OL,7,Fwith a traditional shankh used in
OL,8,Fyogic practices and trained in how to
OL,9,Fuse it properly before taking it home,
OL,10,Fwhile the remaining 14 people were
OL,11,Fasked to carry out deep breathing
OL,12,Fexercises.
OL,14,FBoth groups were encouraged to
OL,15,Fpractice for a minimum of 15 minutes
OL,16,Ffive days a week.
OL,18,FThey were monitored during sleep and
OL,19,Fasked questions about sleep quality
OL,20,Fand how tired they felt during the day.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
