OL,3,CAncient ritual of blowing into shell
OL,4,C'could help with common sleep disorder'
OL,6,FAfter six months, the study found
OL,7,Fthose who practised shankh blowing
OL,8,Freported sleeping better and were 34%
OL,9,Fless sleepy during the day.
OL,11,FThey also had higher levels of oxygen
OL,12,Fin the blood during the night and had
OL,13,Ffour to five fewer apnoeas, where
OL,14,Fbreathing stops during sleep, per hour
OL,15,Fon average.
OL,17,FThey also had higher levels of oxygen
OL,18,Fin their blood during the night.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
