OL,3,CAncient ritual of blowing into shell
OL,4,C'could help with common sleep disorder'
OL,6,FSpeaking of Cpap, Dr Sharma said:
OL,7,F"While effective, many patients find
OL,8,Fit uncomfortable and struggle to use
OL,9,Fit consistently."
OL,11,FHe suggests shankh blowing could be a
OL,12,F"promising alternative".
OL,14,F"Shankh blowing is a simple low-cost,
OL,15,Fbreathing technique that could help
OL,16,Fimprove sleep and reduce symptoms
OL,17,Fwithout the need for machines or
OL,18,Fmedication," Dr Sharma said.
OL,20,FResearchers are now planning a larger
OL,21,Ftrial involving several hospitals.
