OL,3,CAncient ritual of blowing into shell
OL,4,C'could help with common sleep disorder'
OL,6,FDr Sharma added: "This next phase will
OL,7,Fallow us to validate and expand on our
OL,8,Ffindings in a broader, more diverse
OL,9,Fpopulation and assess how shankh
OL,10,Fblowing performs over longer periods.
OL,12,F"We also want to study how this
OL,13,Fpractice affects airway muscle tone,
OL,14,Foxygen levels and sleep in greater
OL,15,Fdetail.
OL,17,F"We're particularly interested in
OL,18,Fcomparing shankh blowing with standard
OL,19,Ftreatments like Cpap, and in examining
OL,20,Fits potential help in more severe
OL,21,Fforms of OSA."
