OL,3,CAncient ritual of blowing into shell
OL,4,C'could help with common sleep disorder'
OL,6,F"This is an intriguing study that
OL,7,Fshows the ancient practice of shankh
OL,8,Fblowing could potentially offer an OSA
OL,9,Ftreatment for selected patients by
OL,10,Ftargeting muscles training.
OL,12,F"A larger study will help provide more
OL,13,Fevidence for this intervention which
OL,14,Fcould be of benefit as a treatment
OL,15,Foption or in combination with other
OL,16,Ftreatments in selected OSA patients."
